package.xml

# LWC configuration files
**/jsconfig.json
**/.eslintrc.json

# LWC Jest
**/__tests__/**

node_modules/

# uiBundle: src/ and build/ are build-time only; dist/ is the deployable output (vite outDir)
**/uiBundles/*/src/**
**/uiBundles/*/build/**
**/uiBundles/*/package.json
**/uiBundles/*/package-lock.json
**/uiBundles/*/vite.config.js
**/uiBundles/*/ui-bundle.json
**/uiBundles/*/codegen.ts
**/uiBundles/*/scripts/**
**/uiBundles/*/node_modules/**
**/uiBundles/*/README.md
